prompts.frontCover:
Vibrant comic book cover illustration, pop art style, featuring Jordan as a superhero named "The INGENIOUS INVENTOR". He is in a dynamic, heroic pose at the center of a chaotic but funny scene, a confident and amused expression on his face. Behind him, a futuristic AIR FRYER, depicted as a "Magical Machine," glows with an ethereal, powerful blue light, with lightning bolts crackling from its sides. Swirling out of the air fryer in a vortex of energy are not just delicious foods, but also mischievous, small, classic-style robots representing AI. One robot is juggling a perfectly cooked fried egg and a bowl of rice. Another robot holds up a Yelp-style sign with 5 stars, pointing towards a delicious-looking ramen bowl also floating in the vortex. In the background, a complex mathematical equation or a logic puzzle is shown on a holographic screen, with a giant green "SOLVED!" checkmark stamped over it. The scene is filled with action lines, "BAM!" and "POW!" sound effect bubbles, and uses a bold, saturated color palette of primary colors like reds, yellows, and blues, with heavy black outlines and Ben-Day dots for shading.

Centered on the card, in a clear space, is the text in a bold, stylized comic book font: "Happy Birthday, Jordan!"
